ps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Melvins-Buzz-Osbourne-and-Nirvanas-Kurt-Cobain.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Melvins-Buzz-Osbourne-and-Nirvanas-Kurt-Cobain-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Melvins-Buzz-Osbourne-and-Nirvanas-Kurt-Cobain-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Melvins-Buzz-Osbourne-and-Nirvanas-Kurt-Cobain-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Melvins-Buzz-Osbourne-and-Nirvanas-Kurt-Cobain-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Melvins-Buzz-Osbourne-and-Nirvanas-Kurt-Cobain-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/melvins">Melvins</a>主唱 Buzz Osborne 解释了为什么他们解雇<a href="/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a>的<a href="/artists/kurt-cobain">Kurt Cobain</a>制作专辑《Houdini》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nirvana-interview-krist-novoselic-in-utero-30-years-ai-music-new-reunion-3501830">Krist Novoselic 谈《In Utero》30 周年以及使用 AI 恢复 Nirvana 音乐</a></strong></li></ul><p>Cobain 被邀请制作 1993 年的专辑，在制作这张 LP 的过程中的某个时刻，梅尔文斯让这位标志性歌手离开了。奥斯本猛烈抨击了长期以来的谣言，称乐队解雇了科本，因为他想为他们写所有的歌曲。</p><p>奥斯本在接受<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ShIjn08fA2Q" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Loudwire</em></a>采访时透露，Nirvana 主唱因毒瘾问题而被解雇：“我们解雇了他，因为他太糟糕了，无法完成唱片工作。”</p><p>在最近接受<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5PEr_9tFfq0" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《左轮手枪》</em></a>采访时被问及是否存在引发分裂的“催化剂时刻”后，奥斯本说：“是的——这正是发生的事情。他没有参加其中一场训练，很明显[他不适合]。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="梅尔文斯 (Melvins) 的巴兹·奥斯本 (Buzz Osborne) 谈《胡迪尼》30 岁时：胡言乱语的歌词、历史悠久的即兴重复、解雇科本等等" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/5PEr_9tFfq0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这位梅尔文斯主唱补充说，这并不是对科本能力的“判断”，而是一种“行不通”的感觉。 “我走进 [Nirvana 经理] 丹尼·戈德堡 (Danny Goldberg) 在大西洋月刊的办公室，告诉了他这一点。他很方便地不记得任何事情，这太疯狂了，”他告诉<em>《左轮手枪》</em> 。</p><p>奥斯本曾于 2009 年与<a href="https://www.thestranger.com/music/2009/05/21/1572742/no-happy-ending"><em>The Stranger</em></a>讨论过这个话题（据<em>Loudwire</em>报道） <em>，</em>他说道：“不幸的是，科本无法创作出任何作品。所以我们进入了录音阶段，我去找Atlantic 的A&amp;R 人员说，‘听着，我不再和他一起录音了。从本质上讲，我要解雇他。就我而言，库尔特已尽其所能，一切就这样结束了。”</p><p>回顾过去的时间和他随后的感受，主唱说：“我对整个营地发生的很多事情感到非常难过。没有一个是好的。在这种情况下，没有太多好的氛围或好的场景。没有幸福的结局。”</p><p> Cobain died by suicide less than a year after the release of &#39;Houdini&#39;. He is credited as co-producer on the album.</p><p> In other news, Nirvana recently announced the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nirvana-announce-special-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-in-utero-3493493">30th anniversary reissue of their seminal album &#39;In Utero.</a> With three super deluxe editions that comprise a total of 72 tracks with 53 previously unreleased live tracks from some of the final live dates from Cobain, bassist Krist Novoselic, drummer Dave Grohl and guitarist Pat Smear, the reissue is set for release on October 27.</p><p> “I&#39;m excited about the live shows on there, because they used AI,” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nirvana-interview-krist-novoselic-in-utero-30-years-ai-music-new-reunion-3501830">Novoselic recently told</a> <em>NME.</em> “We took the digital audio tapes from the soundboard in Rome, Seattle and Los Angeles, then the AI can separate all the instruments and we got a really good mix out of it.”</p><p> Asked if Nirvana ever consider using AI for unreleased Nirvana material, just as <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ringo-starr-last-beatles-song-created-with-ai-beautiful-track-3469906">The Beatles are set to on their upcoming “final track</a> “, he replied: “That&#39;s a good idea! I&#39;m going to bring that up with Dave and Pat! I can hardly wait to hear a new Beatles song. Come on, it&#39;s The Beatles! I want to hear a new Beatles song! And if AI helps it, then absolutely – that&#39;s the way it is today.”</p><p> On if there were any remaining unheard demos or sketches of Nirvana tracks that they could complete, he said: “I don&#39;t know. We&#39;ve got to start talking about this. That&#39;s a good idea. There could be. There&#39;s a point where it&#39;s like, &#39;Is this Nirvana or AI?&#39; There&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-to-ai-creation-of-kurt-cobain-singing-holes-celebrity-skin-3438289">a lot of that stuff already on Youtube</a> , and that&#39;s a debate that&#39;s going to have to be settled when it comes to copyright and disinformation. It&#39;s like <em>2001: A Space Odyssey</em> – &#39;Don&#39;t do it!&#39; ”</p><p> Elsewhere, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-fantomas-reunite-at-the-mr-bungle-and-melvins-tour-closer-3449317">Fantômas reunited on the closing night of the revived &#39;Geek Show&#39; tour</a> featuring <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mr-bungle">Mr. Bungle</a> , Melvins and Spotlights earlier this year.</p><p> Mr. Bungle&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mike-patton">Mike Patton</a> , Trevor Dunn and Dave Lombardo, along with Osborne – all members of the supergroup which formed in 1998 – have been performing on tour together this month, but took to the stage together to reunite Fantômas to close out the run.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/buzz-osborne-explains-why-kurt-cobain-was-fired-from-producing-melvins-album-3509940">Buzz Osborne explains why Kurt Cobain was fired from producing Melvins album</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
